{"tid":1858328,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"即使有人因醫護罷工影響服務而死，我都無條件支持罷工","createTime":"2020-02-02T15:43:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T18:39:04.000Z","uid":324193,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4f0b2ccee04d4479c76fee72c90ea431356083e3","tid":1858328,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:43:58.000Z","msg":"醫護依家面對嘅難題是 <br />\n<br />\n1. 救5個現有嘅病人而不救100個可能因社區爆發而染病嘅人<br />\n<br />\n2. 救100個人，所以罷工要求封關，而犧牲5個現有病人<br />\n<br />\n這是著名的「電車難題」（Trolley problem），醫護要做罷工決定不是一件易事，但我信佢哋做左正確嘅選擇！<br />\n<br />\n最後希望藍絲吾好再blame the victim, 醫護罷工係為左所有人嘅common good, 如果你堅持醫護是做逃兵, 麻煩你立即上火神山醫院幫大陸人，否則麻煩立即收聲"},{"pid":"2e79d477a07c241d94f7e55051e05682d720aaf4","tid":1858328,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T15:57:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"82e16497d2076c0239d3338e3633110e151b2320","tid":1858328,"uid":324193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T16:05:58.000Z","msg":"推2"},{"pid":"1054936af0cc0f651bff6bb19ced8001f5485354","tid":1858328,"uid":171074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T17:28:13.000Z","msg":"+1"},{"pid":"0ade209785f86feaaa09426e2475b3b356e95223","tid":1858328,"uid":171561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T18:04:24.000Z","msg":"呢個其實唔係trolley problem<br />\n<br />\n如果簡左1<br />\n除左救100個社區爆發嘅香港人 功德加10<br />\n仲要救埋冇數個大陸落黎嘅喪屍 功德無量(負數)<br />\n過程中自己病死埋嘅機會仲要大左"},{"pid":"1ed75d89ed3bc4b6cd0ec7c45196f2e6dcdeaa80","tid":1858328,"uid":26876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T18:05:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3be2239d1b940607d2a4ed6de5f9a3261434ee3","tid":1858328,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T18:05:43.000Z","msg":"聽日係第一階段, 打風階段罷工<br />\n緊急服務唔會停, 應該唔會出現咁既情況"},{"pid":"a7593aec7cb0573b97f5001b47419fb09a02c73c","tid":1858328,"uid":262043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T18:06:57.